大家真係要好好多謝佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n份內事 多乜撚？ 咪撚出糧做義工就真係多謝啦</blockquote><br />\n仲要鬼死咁高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf87653a9d6703ce3380f602680d8d641a741b7","tid":454043,"uid":54574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:08:09.000Z","msg":"濫用起訴機制，黑警老屈良好市民！"},{"pid":"55867684f7cb0d5aff892003c36f578ba0d8b1d6","tid":454043,"uid":89349,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實做警察好慘 成日俾d市民玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有起事上黎又要警察幫手<br />\n但佢地都依然繼續做好份工<br />\n大家真係要好好多謝佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2014年10月，我唸好多人都o係旺角，親身見證警察同黑社會公然合作</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d41eb87fa8ede2de32a6636d7c8e5cfb1445b3","tid":454043,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:13:42.000Z","msg":"講開又講，係警署用LAN線自殺單野段CCTV搵到未？？"},{"pid":"abe662c7d341f2a8a04bc7fd88516d8511046f71","tid":454043,"uid":89349,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日黑警前黑警後 真正壞份子只係佔少部份 同埋本身警察嘅職責就係維持治安 無人搞串個party嘅話 警察根本唔會岀手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2014年，旺角街頭，我親眼睇住一個流氓當街非禮女學生，有幾個警察睇住都唔做野。<br />\n<br />\n後來有班後生仔發現，隨之起哄，班差人先走埋來拎警棍，但就係驅散班後生仔<br />\n<br />\n當時我就唸，究竟依班警察有冇啊媽生，佢哋有冇細妹，有冇女朋友?<br />\n<br />\n係咪當左差之後就可以完全埋沒良知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"53759bb5e36241e2b00f83e5047155a228be488e","tid":454043,"uid":52148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"黑警屈人增加左幾多呀,只唔只四倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" cla